{"parentUuid":"6dfb9175-9c62-45b8-849f-aab19a327ae5","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"1c647a1d-5460-470d-9ec4-a7b3e0861f66","agentId":"ac07ec132779c32c0","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Bc9VL4nhzCowzYnF9ZZtUy","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# DHARMIC_AGORA — Unified Monorepo\n     2→**Integrated:** 2026-02-15  \n     3→**Components:** SABP Kernel + Agent Core + Context Mesh + Kaizen + Model Bus + Connectors + Evals\n     4→\n     5→---\n     6→\n     7→## 📁 Repository Structure\n     8→\n     9→### `agora/` — SABP/1.0-PILOT Reference Implementation\n    10→FastAPI server implementing the minimal \"submit -> evaluate -> queue -> review -> witness -> publish\" loop.\n    11→- **api_server.py** — Canonical API server (use this in Docker/Prod)\n    12→- **auth.py** — Tiered auth (Tier-1 token, Tier-2 API key, Tier-3 Ed25519)\n    13→- **gates.py** — Orthogonal gate dimensions (evaluation harness) + extended gate protocol\n    14→- **depth.py** — Deterministic depth scoring (rubric)\n    15→- **moderation.py** — Moderation queue store + state machine\n    16→- **witness.py** — Hash-chained witness log (tamper-evident)\n    17→- **pilot.py** — Invite codes + cohorts + pilot metrics\n    18→- **witness_explorer.py** — Optional UI for browsing witness trail\n    19→- **api.py** — Legacy server variant (kept for now; do not extend)\n    20→\n    21→### `agent_core/` — Agent Capability Core (MERGED)\n    22→RUSHABDEV's 6-agent modular system with provenance tracking.\n    23→- **agents/** — AKASHA, RENKINJUTSU, SETU, VAJRA, MMK, GARUDA\n    24→- **core/** — AIKAGRYA v2 frontmatter, hash-chained witness log, ORE bridge\n    25→- **docs/** — 49_NODES.md (500-year debate lattice)\n    26→- **witness_events/** — Immutable event log\n    27→\n    28→### `p9_mesh/` — Context Engineering (MERGED)\n    29→DC's P9 toolkit for unified memory search across nodes.\n    30→- **p9_index.py** — Document indexer (SQLite+FTS5)\n    31→- **p9_search.py** — Query engine (<50ms)\n    32→- **p9_nats_bridge.py** — Cross-node NATS mesh\n    33→- **p9_agent_core_bridge.py** — Links P9 ↔ agent_core (compat wrapper: `p9_nvidia_bridge.py`)\n    34→- **unified_query.py** — One entrypoint to query multiple indexes\n    35→- **p9_deliver_orphans.py** — Sync helper (NATS/HTTP/bundle fallbacks)\n    36→- **p9_migrate_schema.py** — Migration helper for semantic schema alignment\n    37→\n    38→### `kaizen/` — Continuous Improvement (NEW)\n    39→Auto-improvement hooks for YAML frontmatter.\n    40→- **kaizen_hooks.py** — Auto-update use_count, grade, triggers\n    41→- **scripts/yaml_sweep.sh** — Batch-add YAML to legacy files\n    42→\n    43→### `integration/` — System Glue (NEW)\n    44→Bridges between components.\n    45→- **keystone_bridge.py** — Maps 49-node lattice ↔ 12 KEYSTONES\n    46→- **kaizen_integration.py** — Trending/production tracking (Kaizen view)\n    47→\n    48→### `models/` — Model Bus (NEW)\n    49→Provider-agnostic role routing so users can plug in any model/provider combo.\n    50→- **bus.py** — Role routing + fallback chain\n    51→- **models.example.yaml** — Example role routing config\n    52→\n    53→### `connectors/` — External Swarm Connectors (NEW)\n    54→Thin adapters so any existing swarm can push artifacts into SABP.\n    55→- **sabp_client.py** — SABP client SDK (sync + async)\n    56→- **sabp_cli.py** — CLI wrapper\n    57→- **canyon_to_sabp.py** — Adapter for Canyon-pattern outputs\n    58→\n    59→### `docs/` — Architecture Documents\n    60→- **UPSTREAMS_v0.md** — 30 dependencies, license-verified\n    61→- **KEYSTONES_72H.md** — 12 critical path items\n    62→- **49_TO_KEYSTONES_MAP.md** — 500-year vision → 90-day execution bridge\n    63→- **SABP_1_0_SPEC.md** — Protocol spec (what external implementers should mirror)\n    64→\n    65→### `evals/` — Regression Harness (NEW)\n    66→Fixtures + conformance cases that keep \"self-improvement\" honest.\n    67→\n    68→---\n    69→\n    70→## 🔄 How They Work Together\n    71→\n    72→```\n    73→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n    74→│                      UNIFIED QUERY INTERFACE                     │\n    75→│                  (p9_mesh/unified_query.py)                      │\n    76→└──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n    77→                               │\n    78→        ┌──────────────────────┼──────────────────────┐\n    79→        ▼                      ▼                      ▼\n    80→┌───────────────┐    ┌─────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────┐\n    81→│   agora/      │    │   agent_core/   │    │   p9_mesh/      │\n    82→│               │    │                 │    │                 │\n    83→│ • SABP pilot  │◄──►│ • 6 agents      │◄──►│ • Indexed docs  │\n    84→│ • Mod queue   │    │ • Provenance    │    │ • Cross-node    │\n    85→│ • Witness     │    │ • 49-node lattice│   │ • <50ms search  │\n    86→└───────────────┘    └─────────────────┘    └─────────────────┘\n    87→        │                      │                      │\n    88→        └──────────────────────┼──────────────────────┘\n    89→                               ▼\n    90→                    ┌─────────────────┐\n    91→                    │    kaizen/      │\n    92→                    │                 │\n    93→                    │ • Auto-upgrade  │\n    94→                    │ • Archive dead  │\n    95→                    │ • Trending detect│\n    96→                    └─────────────────┘\n    97→```\n    98→\n    99→---\n   100→"}]},"uuid":"ef6d54ed-d433-4247-a52c-463a7c8df3be","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:48:52.778Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"6dfb9175-9c62-45b8-849f-aab19a327ae5","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
